author: Edited from a Press Release
title: Huntington's Bunny Bombshell at Con
text:
Monday, October 5, 2015 - 15:15 Updated 2 hours ago Edited from a Press Release Huntington cosplayer, Bunny Bombshell, will be exhibiting and participating at the Tsubasacon , Oct. 9-11 at the Big Sandy Superstore Arena. 
Bunny who recently appeared at the Highlands Con (Ashland) and Shock a Con ( Charleston) will debut brand new prints and a new costume. Autographed pictures will be on sale. 
She will be a "United Against Bullying" panelist Saturday evening at 9 p.m. The panel is about bullying cosplayers and how it effects people. They will discuss different types of bullying that can occur.
